{"tid":669460,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[今晚食自己]日式牛肉飯","createTime":"2018-05-18T12:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T08:40:04.000Z","uid":57555,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6b5e962cc45c36a08ff9a880811efe5a52adc84b","tid":669460,"uid":57555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:41:58.000Z","msg":"上網睇過幾個食譜<br />\n跟過黎煮都唔成功<br />\n通常D食譜都教直接放牛肉入過汁度煮<br />\n不過次次都出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次改一下做法試試<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/203606_f4ada10acbd99b8f80eccc34b13b05d8.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F203606_f4ada10acbd99b8f80eccc34b13b05d8.JPG&h=423086af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n肥牛             500g<br />\n津蔥             1個<br />\n薑未             少許<br />\n昆布             4小塊<br />\n鰹魚片         少許<br />\n日本醬油     1湯匙<br />\n味琳            1湯匙"},{"pid":"9564693d4fbdc9a5344560368881c437de7cd725","tid":669460,"uid":57555,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:46:21.000Z","msg":"第一件事係淥下D肥牛，汆汆水<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/204321_e84a4715df7015fa97f11b3d1b9711fb.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F204321_e84a4715df7015fa97f11b3d1b9711fb.JPG&h=a3c18bcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n汆完水嘅湯汁勁多泡沫，非常濁<br />\n如果跟其他食譜，直接用過汁煮牛肉<br />\n個汁會明顥有腥臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁點撈飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4cdb79e2f50ac0e68006772236671feba04e794","tid":669460,"uid":141871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:50:38.000Z","msg":"薑胠腥呀柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"095a232445cef3f4cc81aba2e8601ea23c987f50","tid":669460,"uid":57555,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:51:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/204639_916ed75eaf14ff34db3b48c647988e90.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F204639_916ed75eaf14ff34db3b48c647988e90.JPG&h=a7f98217&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個時候扔4塊昆布落去滾兩下<br />\nD泡沫同污糟野會痴埋一舊舊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/204823_33a2538af92d1aebc27f2d768ee17ca6.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F204823_33a2538af92d1aebc27f2d768ee17ca6.JPG&h=052687fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個湯開始由啡色變為透明<br />\n污糟野開始結塊就得<br />\n唔洗滾好耐<br />\n跟手焜熄火，扔D鰹魚片落去<br />\n上蓋焗佢10分鐘"},{"pid":"628410fd5d7b98759492a9f50d75e16653f9b80b","tid":669460,"uid":57555,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:53:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/205157_090c6a7026b4d8545a7439b5020064b5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F205157_090c6a7026b4d8545a7439b5020064b5.JPG&h=fc38d8da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n焗完10分鐘<br />\n搵個篩隔一隔D污糟野、昆布同鰹魚片<br />\n當堂清左好多"},{"pid":"7d6b9a3e004161693bee34de63d52ed9bdd8096b","tid":669460,"uid":6860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:54:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6438f2295dcf34e55b9f5ec34d7f694f8876df55","tid":669460,"uid":57555,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:59:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/205853_d4f3b6db5a17f9e4514f110426f0d753.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F205853_d4f3b6db5a17f9e4514f110426f0d753.JPG&h=92f4e80d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個時候扔埋D洋蔥、薑末落去<br />\n再加埋果1湯匙日式醬油同1湯匙味琳落去<br />\n煮大概15-20分鐘<br />\n睇你想食D洋蔥幾淋<br />\n有需要就煮耐D<br />\n最後加埋D熟左嘅肥牛，煮一煮佢<br />\n試試味酌量加D鹽糖調味，食得!"},{"pid":"cb47f90084a638f749838fdfc6ad801caf6a24f6","tid":669460,"uid":57555,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b4cdb79e2f50ac0e68006772236671feba04e794","tid":669460,"uid":141871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:50:38.000Z","msg":"薑胠腥呀柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:59:44.000Z","msg":"有落呀巴打<br />\n不過我覺得隔下D湯效果會好D"},{"pid":"ded9ad0edd87347e597a9d8a3108c5206a20c7a4","tid":669460,"uid":57555,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T13:01:00.000Z","msg":"SORRY<br />\n賣相爭D<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都食得落口<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/210047_72d9e9b29e471712e01f9951cf966d24.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F210047_72d9e9b29e471712e01f9951cf966d24.JPG&h=c419054f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3940e299cf1435a7c0ae37bc65d42cdeb2857c8c","tid":669460,"uid":152753,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T14:08:48.000Z","msg":"吉野家好似快手啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"800fe5f374e106e38d9bb9350154dc34382ec3f4","tid":669460,"uid":141871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb47f90084a638f749838fdfc6ad801caf6a24f6","tid":669460,"uid":57555,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b4cdb79e2f50ac0e68006772236671feba04e794","tid":669460,"uid":141871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:50:38.000Z","msg":"薑胠腥呀柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:59:44.000Z","msg":"有落呀巴打<br />\n不過我覺得隔下D湯效果會好D"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:13:09.000Z","msg":"撈左面啲泡就可以直接出啲湯"},{